    • initialize

      private void initialize() throws IOException
      Initialize the High Score List interface and list the top five score.
      抛出:
      IOException - If the target score list file does not exist, then throws exception.

    • onMouseClicked

      void onMouseClicked​(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event) throws IOException
      If click back button, return to the homepage.
      参数:
      event - MouseEvent type, here means mouse click the button.
      抛出:
      IOException - If the target fxml file does not exist, then throw IOException.

    • onMouseEntered

      void onMouseEntered​(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event)
      If the mouse moves over the button, then changes the color of the button to yellow.
      参数:
      event - MouseEvent type, here means mouse moves over the button.

    • onMouseExited

      void onMouseExited​(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event)
      If the mouse moves away from the button, then changes the color of the button to white.
      参数:
      event - MouseEvent type, here means mouse moves away from the button.
